name: FunkyFairyParties
short_description: Themed party services offered by Funky Fairy Parties, Sydney are loaded with fun, surprises, excitement and mystery for young kids of all ages. Girls dance in joy with beautiful fairy entertainers taking them to fantasy trips of mountains and seas. Children are immersed in fun and surprises when tales of their favorite characters of Cinderella, Snow White, Little Mermaid, Sleeping Beauty, Harmony etc are narrated in a fantasizing way. Mysterious yet funny characters of Spider Man, Peter Pan and other themes like pirates and clowns captivate the boys in the party. We offer you an entire range of themes to choose for prince and princess birthday parties.
